Barloworld of South Africa Posts Revenue of $3.4 Billion in the First Half

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-05-17T05:06:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/barloworld-of-south-africa-posts-revenue-of-3-4-billion-in-the-first-half.html
Barloworld Ltd. (BAW)  said it posted first-
half revenue of 23.6 billion rand.  The company commented in a statement to the Stock Exchange
News Service in Johannesburg today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
